  <div class="checklist-disclaimer">
    <p><strong>NON-CONTRACTUAL GUIDANCE</strong></p>
    <p>This checklist is provided as guidance only and does not form part of the tenancy agreement. It summarises key legal obligations for landlords in England. For detailed requirements, consult the relevant legislation or seek professional legal advice.</p>
